'''Aha-erlebnis''' is a [[German language|German]] term, literally meaning 'aha-experience' and referring to the effect of suddenly finding the insight, solution or answer to a problem that has troubled someone for some time. The most famous example is [[Archimedes]]' [[Eureka (word)|Eureka]]!.

